Interface Table

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.hibernate.internal.util.Loggable
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTable, CteTable, DerivedTable, IdTable, PhysicalTable

    public interface Table
extends org.hibernate.internal.util.Loggable
    Represents a table in the mapping in terms of what ANSI SQL calls a "table reference". Specifically, this models the commonality between a physical table reference and a derived table (in-line view).
